title: West Sacramento Hosts Regional Financial Planning Day, Oct. 10 (City of West Sacramento, CA)
text: ( Source : City of West Sacramento, CA ) October 9, 2015 A free financial planning workshop is scheduled for Saturday, Oct. 10 , 9 a.m.-3 p.m. at the West Sacramento City Hall , 1110 West Capitol Ave. Personal financial planning is essential,
